Trade Gothic W01 Light								"LEARN MORE ABOUT THE KANGYUR"
Trade Gothic W01 Light Oblique
Trade Gothic W01 Roman								"TRANSLATING THE WORDS OF THE BUDDHA", 
Trade Gothic W01 Oblique
Trade Gothic W01 Bold								Nav-bar button text, "The Kangyur"
Trade Gothic W01 Bold Oblique
Trade Gothic W01 Bold #2							"Discipline"
Trade Gothic W01 Bold #2 Oblique
Trade Gothic W01 Condensed #18
Trade Gothic W01 Condensed #18 Oblique
